``` [Auth] - Failed Brute Force (single account, no success) — MITRE T1110.001
    Many failures against ONE account from ONE source with no success — brute
    force that never landed. Distinct from spray (many accounts) and from the
    success case. ```
index=auth sourcetype=login_events
| bucket _time span=1d
| stats count(eval(success=0)) AS failures, count(eval(success=1)) AS successes
    BY username, src_ip, _time
| where failures>=10 AND successes=0
| sort - failures
